    'books.series.title': 'Brilliant Women, Remarkable Stories — published in English',
    'books.series.desc': "Six portraits of extraordinary women, told for children. Scientists, adventurers, resisters, queens — figures who shook their era and whose stories deserve to be passed on from the very first pages. Each book, a life. Each life, a lesson.",
